Constructor Detail

Image

public Image(org.json.JSONObject imageObject)
      throws IllegalArgumentException,
             org.json.JSONException
Construct a new image by safely parsing all known image values out of the given JSONObject.

If a property is not available from the JSONObject, it's value is simply set to null and ignored and parsing continues.

Parameters:
imageObject - The JSONObject that will be queried for all the known properties for this image.
Throws:
IllegalArgumentException - if imageObject is null.
org.json.JSONException - if any JSONObject-related exception occurs.

Construct a new image with all the given property values.

Parameters:
id - The ID of the image.
imageKey - The security key for the image.
fileName - The original file name of the image.
caption - The caption for the image.
keywords - Keywords assigned to the image.
position - The position of the image in the album.
date - The timestamp from the image.
format - The file format of the image.
serial - The "version" of the image as edited by SmugMug. Each time an image is edited it's "version" is incremented and is represented by the serial value.
watermark - Used to indicate if the image has a watermark set on it or not.
latitude - The latitude associated with this image (for geo-tagging purposes).
longitude - The longitude associated with this image (for geo-tagging purposes).
altitude - The altitude associated with this image (for geo-tagging purposes).
hidden - A flag indicating if the image is hidden or not.
size - The size, in bytes, of the image.
width - The width of the image;
height - The height of the image;
md5sum - The MD5 Sum of the image.
lastUpdated - The timestamp of the last updated date for the image.
albumURL - A URL for the album this image is contained in.
tinyURL - A URL for a tiny size version of the image.
thumbURL - A URL for a thumbnail size version of the image.
smallURL - A URL for a small size version of the image.
mediumURL - A URL for a medium size version of the image.
largeURL - A URL for a large size version of the image.
xLargeURL - A URL for a x-large size version of the image.
x2LargeURL - A URL for a xx-large size version of the image.
x3LargeURL - A URL for a xxx-large size version of the image.
originalURL - A URL for the original image.
video320URL - A URL for the 320-pixel wide version of this video.
video640URL - A URL for the 640-pixel wide version of this video.
video960URL - A URL for the 960-pixel wide version of this video.
video1280URL - A URL for the 1280-pixel wide version of this video.
album - The Album that this image is contained in.
